<view class="page transit-location-page"><view class="form-header"><view class="form-header-title">上报在途运输位置</view><view class="form-header-desc">请上传托运车辆当前的地理位置，车商客户可实时查看最新轨迹。</view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">定位信息</view><view class="field"><text class="label">当前省市 <text class="required">*</text></text><view class="picker-display" bindtap="{{d}}"><text wx:if="{{a}}">{{b}} · {{c}}</text><text wx:else style="color:#9ca3af">选择当前运输省份与城市</text></view></view><view class="field"><text class="label">详细在途位置/路段 <text class="required">*</text></text><input class="input" placeholder="请输入详细的高速路段/服务区/分拨点" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{e}}" bindinput="{{f}}"/></view><view class="field"><text class="label">GPS 经纬度坐标 <text class="required">*</text></text><view class="row"><input class="input flex-1" type="digit" placeholder="纬度 (Lat)" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{g}}" bindinput="{{h}}"/><input class="input flex-1" type="digit" placeholder="经度 (Lng)" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{i}}" bindinput="{{j}}"/><button class="secondary-btn" style="min-height:88rpx" bindtap="{{k}}">定位</button></view></view><view class="field"><text class="label">备注说明</text><block wx:if="{{r0}}"><textarea class="textarea" placeholder="可在此备注当前天气、交通堵塞等特殊在途情况" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{l}}" bindinput="{{m}}"/></block></view></view><region-picker wx:if="{{p}}" class="r" u-r="regionPicker" bindselect="{{o}}" u-i="279348e8-0" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{p}}"/><view class="fixed-footer"><button class="primary-btn animate-btn" loading="{{q}}" bindtap="{{r}}"> 上报当前最新位置 </button></view></view>